reviewText: My husband and I love CSI Miami and appreciate being able to get the first eight seasons in this set.  Being avid watchers, we are currently in the midst of season 6 already.  The only problem so far with this set is with the case for the season 5 DVD's; that case arrived broken in the center so that discs 2 and 3 always fall out when the case is opened--the discs can't be held securely in place.  So that case needs replacement.  We didn't mention this to the seller before now because we're waiting to see if the rest of the set is OK.
summary: Thank You for Bringing Us CSI Miami
